{"tid":2291491,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"鼠王芬都buy鄭松泰觀點同口味　美心蛋糕賀60大壽","createTime":"2020-11-18T23:05:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-19T11:39:24.000Z","uid":271829,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"0af2f3c3758800c185b9532f123730ec00744219","tid":2291491,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T23:05:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/XRi0NyFgd5s-qmTTIfPJzWh5AeE=/1950x1097/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/PUNB4SP3T5HYRKUEIKFN2MJIEQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FXRi0NyFgd5s-qmTTIfPJzWh5AeE%3D%2F1950x1097%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FPUNB4SP3T5HYRKUEIKFN2MJIEQ.png&h=5da274d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n梁美芬合埋眼同雙手合十咁，對住美心整嘅BAILEYS奶酒蛋糕許願，慶祝60大壽，同鄭松泰半個月前po嗰幅一模一樣。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/QuTrFNprDTiFRbIJEr_9IIs-v0s=/1950x1097/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/6EJV2CZKBZBYHCUUMEMTDDVXJU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FQuTrFNprDTiFRbIJEr_9IIs-v0s%3D%2F1950x1097%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F6EJV2CZKBZBYHCUUMEMTDDVXJU.jpg&h=4b462db6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n梁美芬話同意鄭松泰觀點，就係政府缺乏規劃。估唔到喎，建制派都會同意非建制派講嘢嘅？<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n立法會今日又渡過咗無主流民主派嘅一日，好可惜，議會效率仲係欠奉，竟然未能夠喺一日內完成晒所有議程，即係聽朝9點仍然要復會，繼續辯論由工聯會陸頌雄提出、有關紓緩道路交通擠塞嘅無約束力議案，而且罕有地，有建制派議員認同非建制派熱血公民鄭松泰嘅發言添。<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201118/IBHODFDIMBDYZGG3J7OCKZF5GE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201118%2FIBHODFDIMBDYZGG3J7OCKZF5GE%2F&d=VbAd486K8RrC2DEUtq3b5ilkmYPKinjppKJkD7WQ61o%3D&h=4f7b1d10\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201118%2FIBHODFDIMBDYZGG3J7OCKZF5GE%2F&h=8064f7b0\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201118/IBHODFDIMBDYZGG3J7OCKZF5GE/</a><br />\n<br />\n相關報道：鄭松泰生日食美心蛋糕被狙擊 反斥「黃絲不可理喻」<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201105/RODZOB5QKRGXVCDK4C674NMWEY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201105%2FRODZOB5QKRGXVCDK4C674NMWEY%2F&d=VbAd486K8RrC2DEUtq3b5ilkmYPKinjppKJkD7WQ61o%3D&h=dcf19509\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201105%2FRODZOB5QKRGXVCDK4C674NMWEY%2F&h=5f37e74d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201105/RODZOB5QKRGXVCDK4C674NMWEY/</a>"},{"pid":"74ce5b67ffbe438b0a4272bf930dba032985f8e7","tid":2291491,"uid":59522,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T23:12:16.000Z","msg":"食美心已經抵死<br />\n蟲泰同條臭西一擔擔扮乜清高"},{"pid":"ed9bbb7a380c3c3a6ac848153c3274c0e0068749","tid":2291491,"uid":161011,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T23:15:17.000Z","msg":"兩隻不同品種嘅共狗"},{"pid":"66baf8d6d937215f3c88d6f8a3d6be8644188de9","tid":2291491,"uid":312363,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T23:15:20.000Z","msg":"心有靈犀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6b71f18239ac8787aecee8899c8a8a3e17ae3ae","tid":2291491,"uid":20867,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ed9bbb7a380c3c3a6ac848153c3274c0e0068749","tid":2291491,"uid":161011,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T23:15:17.000Z","msg":"兩隻不同品種嘅共狗"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T23:22:32.000Z","msg":"呢兩隻共狗點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20100525/photo/0525-00174-001b1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20100525%2Fphoto%2F0525-00174-001b1.jpg&h=e54ca17b&s={SI